The paper deals with the problem of car detection from aerial images using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN), which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of CNNs also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the impact of various factors such as UAV's altitude and camera resolution, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper involves image processing and analysis, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
